                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. High chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the evening. Winds east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h turning northerly during the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to around 13 with daytime temperatures reaching the low to mid 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-04-06T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-07T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-05T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-06T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 17 with daytime temperatures reaching the mid to high 20s.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-04-07T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-08T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-06T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-07T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southerly during the morning then becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 14 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
